tion><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/20130506/featured.png"/></item><item><title>评估报告：机会只有 50%</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/pgbg/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2013 19:41:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/pgbg/</guid><description>电商业务缺乏 ERP 系统如同跑车开山路般低效，砍掉分销渠道更是雪上加霜。团购成本高且资金审批难，团队执行力强但决策阻力大。功劳归他人、失误自己扛，时间成本是最大风险。成功概率五五开，关键在于关系磨合而非贸然行动！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/pgbg/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>